1
00:03:28,901 --> 00:03:34,203
How many times have l told you not
to touch me from behind?

2
00:03:34,573 --> 00:03:36,871
l consider anybody touching me
from behind to be my enemy.

3
00:03:37,910 --> 00:03:39,912
Fortunately l'd brush in my hand.

4
00:03:39,912 --> 00:03:43,871
Had l a knife or pistol
you would have been lying dead.

5
00:03:44,917 --> 00:03:47,586
Tell me, what's the matter?

6
00:03:47,586 --> 00:03:50,589
Party has come to buy weapons and
RDX. May l bring him here tomorrow

7
00:03:50,589 --> 00:03:53,888
No ! Not here.
l never do business from here.

8
00:03:54,593 --> 00:03:57,562
Here l'm a sculptor.

9
00:03:58,931 --> 00:04:03,936
l make beautiful sculptures.
What l hide in them, only l know.

10
00:04:03,936 --> 00:04:08,941
Where will you meet him?
- ln the hotel. ln any room.

11
00:04:08,941 --> 00:04:12,945
What if l'm caught doing
business here.

12
00:04:12,945 --> 00:04:16,949
l'm very fearful of being
beaten by the police.

13
00:04:16,949 --> 00:04:18,917
They hang upside down
and turn stick on you.

14
00:04:23,956 --> 00:04:25,958
l hear two new inspectors
have come.

15
00:04:25,958 --> 00:04:27,960
Arjun Singh and Pyarelal.

16
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:30,929
Don't know how are they !

17
00:05:00,993 --> 00:05:02,961
What's going on?

18
00:05:06,999 --> 00:05:10,669
Can't you see me
sharpening the saw?

19
00:05:10,669 --> 00:05:14,006
You take me for an idiot !

20
00:05:14,006 --> 00:05:17,676
What is there to take you for?
You are an idiot.

21
00:05:17,676 --> 00:05:21,680
Hey ... ! l know everything.

22
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:27,019
You are panning to escape -
You must take me too.

23
00:05:27,019 --> 00:05:31,023
Hey, are you out of your mind?

24
00:05:31,023 --> 00:05:34,982
My mind is perfectly sound but if
it goes bad, l start shouting.

25
00:05:39,031 --> 00:05:43,991
Hey, why are you doing that?
- You too can tag along with us.

26
00:05:45,037 --> 00:05:49,041
Why are you being jealous if your
two brothers are trying to escape.

27
00:05:49,041 --> 00:05:53,045
lf three brothers escape together
that will make me very happy.

28
00:05:53,045 --> 00:05:58,050
Do you want to swallow the rice
that we have cooked?

29
00:05:58,050 --> 00:06:02,054
We have worked for four nights
to cut these bars.

30
00:06:02,054 --> 00:06:05,057
And you want ...
- to get out so easily.

31
00:06:05,057 --> 00:06:09,016
Hey Head Constable ... !
- Okay you too come along quietly.

32
00:06:43,095 --> 00:06:45,097
We've come out of the jail.

33
00:06:45,097 --> 00:06:47,099
But the city must have
been cordoned off.

34
00:06:47,099 --> 00:06:49,101
We can't even buy
a change of clothes.

35
00:06:49,101 --> 00:06:55,107
You helped me escape, so it's now
my duty to help you somehow.

36
00:06:55,107 --> 00:06:58,076
Ha ! How can you help us -
Your own brain needs fixing.

37
00:06:58,777 --> 00:07:04,116
l'll take you to my boss who can
send you out of country overnight.

38
00:07:04,116 --> 00:07:07,119
Tell me something about your boss.
- Shall l tell you his name?

39
00:07:07,119 --> 00:07:09,087
Yes !
- Sunder Kala.

40
00:07:10,122 --> 00:07:15,127
Welcome, Karim.
Sundar Kala is proud of his men.

41
00:07:15,127 --> 00:07:20,132
Like a lion my men can
finish the enemies.

42
00:07:20,132 --> 00:07:22,134
And like a bird they can
fly out of the jail.

43
00:07:22,134 --> 00:07:27,139
Look at him. We did all the work
and praise goes to him.

44
00:07:27,139 --> 00:07:31,098
Speak up !
- lt'll take time to explain.

45
00:07:34,146 --> 00:07:37,149
They are very useful.
The helped me escape from jail.

46
00:07:37,149 --> 00:07:39,151
You can keep them.
They are very useful.

47
00:07:39,151 --> 00:07:43,110
Fine ! lf you say, l'll keep them.
You both are appointed.

48
00:07:46,158 --> 00:07:50,162
Boss ! We've been surrounded
by the police.

49
00:07:50,162 --> 00:07:53,131
Don't move !
Nobody should move from his place.

50
00:07:54,166 --> 00:07:57,169
Don't try anything clever
Sundar Kala !

51
00:07:57,169 --> 00:07:58,796
All my men are armed with gun in
hand and a pistol in pocket.

52
00:07:59,171 --> 00:08:03,175
Your men have rifle -
you don't have any !

53
00:08:03,175 --> 00:08:08,135
lt's cheating. You've too !
l've none. Give me one.

54
00:08:10,849 --> 00:08:12,851
Why do you want to blacken your
clean hands by killing him?

55
00:08:12,851 --> 00:08:14,853
l can take care of him for you.

56
00:08:14,853 --> 00:08:17,822
First you jailed us
now you want to jail Sunder !

57
00:08:21,193 --> 00:08:26,198
Give us a chance to show loyalty.
You give these revolvers to us.

58
00:08:26,198 --> 00:08:28,867
You give us order and then see.
- Fine, take this

59
00:08:28,867 --> 00:08:32,826
Now order us.
- Kill him.

60
00:08:36,875 --> 00:08:39,878
Hey Karim ! Have they gone mad ?

61
00:08:39,878 --> 00:08:41,213
Hey what you kids are doing ?

62
00:08:41,213 --> 00:08:46,218
lf you pull the trigger, the brain
of boss will come out of his cap.

63
00:08:46,218 --> 00:08:49,221
We escaped from jail to
catch your boss !

64
00:08:49,221 --> 00:08:51,223
That's why we brought
you here, idiot !

65
00:08:51,223 --> 00:08:54,226
That's cheating !
- lt isn't cheating, it's setting.

66
00:08:54,226 --> 00:08:56,228
But who are these two?

67
00:08:56,228 --> 00:09:03,235
Meet me ! l'm lnspector
Arjun Singh.

68
00:09:03,235 --> 00:09:06,204
And l'm lnspector Pyare Mohan.

69
00:09:10,242 --> 00:09:14,246
You deliberately punched
me all over.

70
00:09:14,246 --> 00:09:18,250
Sundar Kala had his revolvers
aimed at your temples.

71
00:09:18,250 --> 00:09:21,253
Had we not punched you in time,
he'd have shot into your temples

72
00:09:21,253 --> 00:09:24,256
lnstead of warming, your family
would've been weeping by now.

73
00:09:24,256 --> 00:09:28,260
Even if you're getting any warmth
that would be from funeral pyre.

74
00:09:28,260 --> 00:09:30,262
And forgive sir, we'd have been
standing there to salute you.

75
00:09:30,262 --> 00:09:32,264
Why do you keep talking about
the death that hasn't come?

76
00:09:32,264 --> 00:09:35,267
We aren't talking about death -
we are talking about saving you.

77
00:09:35,267 --> 00:09:38,937
We risked our life to save you and
we also caught the criminals.

78
00:09:38,937 --> 00:09:41,273
lnstead of appreciating it you're
weeping over a couple of punches !

79
00:09:41,273 --> 00:09:44,276
Go ! Get out of here and don't
show me your faces.

80
00:09:44,276 --> 00:09:47,279
How can we do that. We get paid
for showing our faces to you.

81
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:51,238
l beg of you, l give you 2-day
vacation, please go from here.

82
00:10:08,634 --> 00:10:10,969
Don't talk with me.
You're late again.

83
00:10:10,969 --> 00:10:14,306
What can l do. Man l come with
drives jeep like a bullock-cart.

84
00:10:14,306 --> 00:10:17,976
You never come alone. You always
bring some excuses with you.

85
00:10:17,976 --> 00:10:20,274
l think l'd stop seeing you.
- What do you mean.

86
00:10:20,979 --> 00:10:23,277
l mean, l should marry you.

87
00:10:26,318 --> 00:10:30,322
l too want this. But how to
explain this to my brother?

88
00:10:30,322 --> 00:10:32,324
He's growing older, but he
doesn't care what happens to me.

89
00:10:32,324 --> 00:10:38,330
You mean, l can't marry you too.
- Perhaps ... !

90
00:10:38,330 --> 00:10:40,332
What do you mean by perhaps.
Tell your mom to marry him !

91
00:10:40,332 --> 00:10:44,336
What ?
- Your mom should get him married.

92
00:10:44,336 --> 00:10:47,339
lf he gets married -
then l get married.

93
00:10:47,339 --> 00:10:53,345
l'm afraid what your brother will
think if he finds out about us.

94
00:10:53,345 --> 00:10:56,314
He always wrong opinion about me.
Perhaps l'm little big naught ... !

95
00:10:57,349 --> 00:10:59,351
l want to file a complaint
against Arjun Singh.

96
00:10:59,351 --> 00:11:01,353
What is my crime?

97
00:11:01,353 --> 00:11:03,355
He has not yet married.

98
00:11:03,355 --> 00:11:07,359
See ... we're a small happy
family of three members.

99
00:11:07,359 --> 00:11:09,361
My mother, my sister and l.

100
00:11:09,361 --> 00:11:13,365
When the fourth member comes -
who knows what her nature will be.

101
00:11:13,365 --> 00:11:16,368
Will she be able to run this home?
Will she serve my mother or not?

102
00:11:16,368 --> 00:11:18,370
l want to avoid these problems.

103
00:11:18,370 --> 00:11:20,372
You can't escape by
such arguments.

104
00:11:20,372 --> 00:11:22,374
lf every man thinks like him there
would be no marriage in this world

105
00:11:22,374 --> 00:11:25,377
From youth till old age
girls will remain unmarried.

106
00:11:25,377 --> 00:11:27,045
World will end.

107
00:11:27,045 --> 00:11:32,384
After hearing arguments from both
sides, Home Minister concludes ...

108
00:11:32,384 --> 00:11:34,386
that either you select a girl of
your own choice and marry her ...

109
00:11:34,386 --> 00:11:36,388
or l will do that by force.

110
00:11:36,388 --> 00:11:40,347
Look at your age. After sometime
we'll hesitate to ask any girl.

111
00:11:41,393 --> 00:11:46,398
As you like. lf the proceeding is
over, can l get something to eat.

112
00:11:46,398 --> 00:11:49,367
lf you're ready for marriage -
then food is also ready, brother.

113
00:11:53,405 --> 00:11:57,409
lt's so nice food ... !
My respects mom.

114
00:11:57,409 --> 00:12:01,413
Live long. Sit and eat.
- See a mother's heart.

115
00:12:01,413 --> 00:12:04,416
When kids eat - a mother's
heart is delighted.

116
00:12:04,416 --> 00:12:08,086
And there are some people
who become jealous.

117
00:12:08,086 --> 00:12:10,088
How dare you come to this house !

118
00:12:10,088 --> 00:12:13,091
What're you doing -
let him eat.

119
00:12:13,091 --> 00:12:16,428
You live alone Mumbai - you
should always come here to eat.

120
00:12:16,428 --> 00:12:18,430
l think l'd have breakfast too.

121
00:12:18,430 --> 00:12:22,434
lf a man takes good breakfast his
entire day passes pleasantly.

122
00:12:22,434 --> 00:12:24,436
Okay then you should come here
for breakfast every day.

123
00:12:24,436 --> 00:12:28,440
Put a bed for me. l'll leave
for work after breakfast.

124
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:30,442
Get out ...

125
00:12:30,442 --> 00:12:32,444
l'm being insulted ...
- What're you doing ... ?

126
00:12:32,444 --> 00:12:35,447
lf you love him so much,
have some food sent to his house.

127
00:12:35,447 --> 00:12:38,450
Why do you treat him like this?
What evil do you see in him?

128
00:12:38,450 --> 00:12:42,454
The evil that l see in him,
you can't see ... !

129
00:12:42,454 --> 00:12:44,422
Just a minute ...
You bring my meals.

130
00:12:50,462 --> 00:12:56,468
Very good. Excellent.
You've many good weapons.

131
00:12:56,468 --> 00:12:59,471
But this time it is going to
be a very big order.

132
00:12:59,471 --> 00:13:01,439
How big will be the order?

133
00:13:02,474 --> 00:13:05,477
Ten times bigger than
the last order.

134
00:13:05,477 --> 00:13:08,480
Even if it is twenty times bigger,
Zorawar can easily handle it.

135
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:10,448
Really ! Superb !

136
00:13:11,483 --> 00:13:19,447
Mr. Zorawar, you've a big bungalow
why do you have meeting in hotel?

137
00:13:20,158 --> 00:13:24,162
Why are hotels meant for?
For meetings among people like us.

138
00:13:24,162 --> 00:13:27,165
Book a room in anybody's name -
and just close the door.

139
00:13:27,165 --> 00:13:30,502
What goes on behind the
closed door - nobody will know.

140
00:13:30,502 --> 00:13:33,471
This room has been booked in the
name of Jamshed.

141
00:13:34,506 --> 00:13:36,508
You'll ask who's Jamshed.

142
00:13:36,508 --> 00:13:40,512
When l don't know -
how will the police know?

143
00:13:40,512 --> 00:13:42,514
l am afraid of the Mumbai police.

144
00:13:42,514 --> 00:13:45,517
They beat with canes.

145
00:13:45,517 --> 00:13:48,520
l am not afraid of death.
l am afraid of the police.

146
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:59,531
What happened?
- l want to go to bathroom.

147
00:13:59,531 --> 00:14:22,554
Open this door.
- lt has ''Don't disturb'' tab.

148
00:14:22,554 --> 00:14:26,558
Come on, open.
- l can't open.

149
00:14:26,558 --> 00:14:29,527
Don't open the mouth.
Open the door.

150
00:14:36,568 --> 00:14:38,570
What are you doing brother?

151
00:14:38,570 --> 00:14:40,572
Are you watching
a super-hit competition.

152
00:14:40,572 --> 00:14:43,575
What do you want to do?
Want to get me arrested !

153
00:14:43,575 --> 00:14:45,577
Don't you know l'm very
afraid of the police.

154
00:14:45,577 --> 00:14:47,579
Just give me the videocassette.

155
00:14:47,579 --> 00:14:52,584
Zorawar ! This is proof of your
black deeds. You won't be saved.

156
00:14:52,584 --> 00:14:57,544
l've pain in neck so l can't bend.
Give me videocassette - quick.

157
00:14:58,256 --> 00:15:01,593
As long as l am alive
you won't get this cassette.

158
00:15:01,593 --> 00:15:03,561
Maybe l'll take it after
you are dead.

159
00:15:06,598 --> 00:15:11,603
You're lucky.
He was watching it on TV.

160
00:15:11,603 --> 00:15:14,606
You've seen the live telecast.

161
00:15:14,606 --> 00:15:19,611
What should l do to you.
lt is not your age to die.

162
00:15:19,611 --> 00:15:22,580
And your body is too delicate
for putting a bullet in it.

163
00:15:39,398 --> 00:15:41,366
Look ... your confusion and
shaking won't serve any purpose.

164
00:15:41,633 --> 00:15:43,635
A police inspector was
murdered in that hotel.

165
00:15:43,635 --> 00:15:46,638
And l can't forgive the murderer
of my inspector.

166
00:15:46,638 --> 00:15:48,606
Give your complete statement.
- Yes ...

167
00:15:49,307 --> 00:15:51,643
ls this the way to talk
with a girl?

168
00:15:51,643 --> 00:15:53,611
l know our inspector has died,
but this girl is so perplexed ...

169
00:15:54,646 --> 00:15:56,648
l'm taking her statement ...

170
00:15:56,648 --> 00:15:58,616
You first have some water.

171
00:16:06,658 --> 00:16:09,627
Speak up ...
- Yes.

172
00:16:29,347 --> 00:16:34,649
Had l not run, he would
have killed me too.

173
00:16:35,687 --> 00:16:39,646
Don't be afraid.
Police is with you.

174
00:16:40,692 --> 00:16:42,694
We're with you. Don't worry.

175
00:16:42,694 --> 00:16:49,701
lf you see that man again -
can you recognize him?

176
00:16:49,701 --> 00:16:51,703
We're not going to bother
you any more.

177
00:16:51,703 --> 00:16:53,705
Just write your phone
number on this pad.

178
00:16:53,705 --> 00:16:56,708
After we find the murderer,
we'll contact you.

179
00:16:56,708 --> 00:16:58,710
Come on, l'll take you home.

180
00:16:58,710 --> 00:17:01,713
At this time she needs a friend
rather than a police officer.

181
00:17:01,713 --> 00:17:04,682
Don't think you can do it better
than me. You come with me.

182
00:17:13,725 --> 00:17:16,728
Do you live alone in this city?

183
00:17:16,728 --> 00:17:20,687
No sir. My friend Neha lives
with me. Just there ...

184
00:17:24,736 --> 00:17:29,741
So, you live here.
- Yes. My flat is over there.

185
00:17:29,741 --> 00:17:34,746
Okay. l'll now go. When you catch
murderer, call me to recognize him

186
00:17:34,746 --> 00:17:37,749
l helped you, entertained you from
police station to here -

187
00:17:37,749 --> 00:17:40,752
Just to hear this !
- Sorry. Did l say anything wrong?

188
00:17:40,752 --> 00:17:42,720
You broke my heart.

189
00:17:44,422 --> 00:17:46,424
Will we meet only after
we find the criminal?

190
00:17:46,424 --> 00:17:48,426
l don't get you !

191
00:17:48,426 --> 00:17:51,763
Would you mind if l invite you
for tea or dinner? Would you?

192
00:17:51,763 --> 00:17:54,732
Of course not.
You have my phone number.

193
00:17:57,769 --> 00:18:00,738
lf you're afraid or suspect
anyone, give us a call.

194
00:18:07,445 --> 00:18:11,783
Madhu ! Why did you take so long.
l was so worried.

195
00:18:11,783 --> 00:18:13,785
l called you at hotel and found
somebody had been murdered.

196
00:18:13,785 --> 00:18:17,789
A police inspector was in a hotel
room. He was murdered.

197
00:18:17,789 --> 00:18:19,791
Who did it?

198
00:18:19,791 --> 00:18:23,128
l saw the murderer. l went to
police station to report.

199
00:18:23,128 --> 00:18:25,130
How did you come from there?

200
00:18:25,130 --> 00:18:28,133
Pyare dropped me ...
- Pyare ?

201
00:18:28,133 --> 00:18:31,136
Yes ... lnspector Pyare Mohan.

202
00:18:31,136 --> 00:18:35,140
Gem of inspector ! l was
frightened to see the murder ...

203
00:18:35,140 --> 00:18:36,808
but he calmed me and set my mood ...

204
00:18:36,808 --> 00:18:40,812
He was very nice and we
developed good friendship.

205
00:18:40,812 --> 00:18:44,482
He'll phone someday and invite
me for tea or dinner.

206
00:18:44,482 --> 00:18:48,820
You'll eat when you're invited but
l'm starving because of you.

207
00:18:48,820 --> 00:18:51,789
Serve the food - l'll join you.
- Come fast.

208
00:19:05,837 --> 00:19:14,802
Oh my child, my baby, my favorite
kid ... at last l found you dear !

209
00:19:15,847 --> 00:19:21,853
lt has taken burden off my chest.
l searched you everywhere.

210
00:19:21,853 --> 00:19:24,822
And you were reporting to police.
You were giving your statement.

211
00:19:25,857 --> 00:19:28,860
l'm so afraid of police.

212
00:19:28,860 --> 00:19:32,819
He can't sleep. He can't eat.
And you're having nice dinner.

213
00:19:33,865 --> 00:19:38,825
Food is served ...
lt is so tasty.

214
00:19:40,872 --> 00:19:43,875
What are your plans for this girl?

215
00:19:43,875 --> 00:19:45,877
She must be killed.
l've no other choice.

216
00:19:45,877 --> 00:19:47,879
She too understands.

217
00:19:47,879 --> 00:19:49,847
Shall we eat something ?
- Yes, let's eat.

218
00:20:07,899 --> 00:20:11,858
One witness is not yet dead -
another has come to die !

219
00:20:15,907 --> 00:20:17,875
Where did she fall ?
- She ran away.

220
00:20:18,910 --> 00:20:21,879
Go and get her, else she too
will go to police.

221
00:20:49,941 --> 00:20:53,900
Where did she vanish ?

222
00:21:23,641 --> 00:21:26,940
She had a friend, Neha.
Find out where is Neha.

223
00:21:35,987 --> 00:21:37,989
l want to talk with
Pyare Mohan.

224
00:21:37,989 --> 00:21:40,958
He is not here, but you seem to be
worried. Tell me. l can help.

225
00:21:41,659 --> 00:21:44,958
l'll tell Pyare Mohan only ...
- You tell me. Don't hesitate.

226
00:21:45,997 --> 00:21:50,001
l'm Madhu's friend
l've seen her murderer.

227
00:21:50,001 --> 00:21:54,631
Tell me more about ...
- l'll tell Pyare Mohan only.

228
00:21:55,673 --> 00:21:58,301
Pyare Mohan is here.
He just came.

229
00:21:58,676 --> 00:22:00,678
Some girl is calling.
She has witnessed Madhu's murder.

230
00:22:00,678 --> 00:22:02,013
She wants to talk with
